                    </div>
                    <span>I should have read this book BEFORE my recent trip on Southwest.  I actually saw many of the shennanigans Marty describes with such classy humor.  It made me wonder just how many of them he had pulled on me as the middle person to his aisle seat.  The book makes flying Southwest more fun.</span>
                  
